    <div class="Activity.name">Two Containers</div>
    <div class="im_statement"><p>Here is a picture of two containers of colored water.</p>

<p>[<strong>IMAGE NEEDED</strong>: Picture showing two graduated cylinders&#x2014;one with 5 ml of blue water and one with 15 ml of yellow water&#x2014;and a label below each container]</p>

<ol>
	<li>What do you notice about the colored water? Make 1&#x2013;2 observations.</li>
	<li>What would happen if we mix the blue water and yellow water together?</li>
	<li>What would happen if we mix more blue water with the same amount of yellow water?</li>
</ol>
